---
import '../css/global.css'
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Soroban Abundance Token</title>
  <meta property="og:title" content="ðŸŒ³ Soroban Abundance Token">
  <meta property="og:description" content="A Soroban Fungible token that you can mint to yourself">
  <link rel="icon" href="/img/favicon.ico" />
  <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/img/android-chrome-192x192.png" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="/img/social-preview.png">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://ahalabs.dev/abundance-token">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://ahalabs.dev/abundance-token/social-preview.png">
</head>
<body>
  <nav style="position: absolute; right: 0.5em; top: 0.5em; z-index: 2">
    <div id="menu" class="dropdown" aria-live="polite" style="font-size: 0.8em">
      <button class="menu-icon" aria-controls="menu">
        <div></div>
        <span class="visually-hidden">menu</span>
      </button>
      <div class="right" style="width: 7em">
        <div>
          <a href="https://github.com/AhaLabs/abundance-token">View source</a>
        </div>
        <div data-behavior="signed-in" style="display: none; margin-top: 0.5em">
          <button class="link" data-behavior="logout">
            Sign out
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main style="margin: 0 auto; max-width: 50em">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 2rem auto 5rem; max-width: 25em">
      <h1 class="title">Abundance Token</h1>
      <p>
        An non-scarce <a href="https://soroban.stellar.org/" rel="nofollow">Soroban</a> <a href="https://soroban.stellar.org/docs/reference/interfaces/token-interface" rel="nofollow">Fungible Token</a>. Go ahead and take as much as you want!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div data-behavior="gettingStarted">
      <h1>Let's get you set up</h1>
      <p>
        You'll need a few things to get started. Don't worry, it's easy!
      </p>
      <div class="todo-cards">
        <div id="getFreighter">
          <h2>1. Get Freighter</h2>
          <p>
            Freighter is a browser extension that lets you interact with the
            Soroban network. It's like MetaMask, but for Soroban.
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://www.freighter.app/">Get Freighter</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div id="enableFreighter">
          <h2>2. Enable Freighter</h2>
          <p>
            Once you've installed Freighter, you'll need to enable it for this
            site. You can do that by clicking the Freighter icon in your browser
            toolbar.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div id="getTestXLM">
          <h2>3. Get Test XLM</h2>
          <p>
            You'll need a small amount of test XLM to pay for the transaction
            that mints your <span data-behavior="tokenSymbol">ðŸ¤”</span> tokens.
            You can get some from the
            <a href="https://TODO">TODO faucet</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div data-behavior="readyToGo" style="display: none">
      <h1 class="title">
        Your <span data-behavior="tokenSymbol">ðŸ¤”</span> Balance:
        <span class="balance" data-behavior="tokenBalance">ðŸ¤”</span>
      </h1>
      <form style="margin: 0 auto; max-width: 15em">
        <fieldset id="fieldset">
          <label
            for="amount"
            style="display: block; margin: 2em 0 0.1em"
          >
            Want more?
          </label>
          <div style="display: flex">
            <input
              autocomplete="off"
              id="amount"
              type="number"
            />
            <button id="submit" disabled style="border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0">
              OK
            </button>
          </div>
        </fieldset>
      </form>
    </div>

  </main>

  <script src="../js/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
